
*** Working with processes ***
An instance of the program is called as processe.
There can be multiple processes.

1. top  -list the processes.
2. To run the program instance ref. example- firefox+enter 
3. To send program instance background - bg firefox
4. To send program instance forground - fg firfox
4. pidof firefox  -To check process id.
5. kill 6346  -To kill process instance.


